data.description: Back on market due to buyer's financing. Welcome Home! Located in the desired gated Otter Creek area this rare opportunity to own a corner lot home awaits you in a quiet park like environment. Outlet mall shopping, dining options, community pool, tennis, walking trails and other amenities. With a  NEW ROOF & WINDOWS in '23, 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, fireplace for family fun, dining and an eat-in kitchen, stainless steel appliances, tons of cabinet space, large loft upstairs for the at home worker, updated bathrooms, some new light fixtures with a deck and back yard made for entertaining. This should be yours. Contact the listing agent today to for further information or to schedule your private showing.
